@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<div class="container mt-5">
    
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-md-10 text-center">
            <h1 class="display-4 text-success">About VitalVues</h1> 
            <p class="lead text-muted mt-4">
                Empowering users to understand their bloodwork, make informed decisions, and take control of their health.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

   
    <div class="row justify-content-center mt-5">
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card shadow-sm border-0 mb-4">
                <div class="card-body text-center">
                    <h3 class="text-success">Our Mission</h3>
                    <p class="text-muted">
                        To provide users with immediate and clear explanations of their bloodwork results, giving them the tools and knowledge to manage their health effectively.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card shadow-sm border-0 mb-4">
                <div class="card-body text-center">
                    <h3 class="text-success">Our Vision</h3>
                    <p class="text-muted">
                        To create a future where everyone can understand their medical information and take proactive steps toward a healthier lifestyle, assisted by AI-powered insights.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card shadow-sm border-0 mb-4">
                <div class="card-body text-center">
                    <h3 class="text-success">Our Values</h3>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled text-muted">
                        <li> Clarity in medical information</li>
                        <li> Empowerment through knowledge</li>
                        <li> Personalized health support</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row justify-content-center mt-5">
        <div class="col-md-10">
            <div class="card shadow-lg border-0">
                <div class="card-body p-5">
                    <h2 class="text-success mb-4">Problem Statement</h2> 
                    <p class="lead text-muted mb-5">
                        Many people receive blood work results without fully understanding what the results mean. Often, they have to wait for a doctor to explain the findings, which can cause anxiety. Our program is designed to change that by providing immediate, easy-to-understand explanations for each test result.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-muted">
                        By using our system, users can quickly grasp their health status and be better informed when speaking with healthcare professionals. This empowers them to take control of their health, without the uncertainty of waiting.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row justify-content-center mt-5">
        <div class="col-md-10">
            <div class="card shadow-lg border-0">
                <div class="card-body p-5">
                    <h2 class="text-success mb-4">What We Offer</h2>
                    <p class="text-muted">
                        In addition to simplifying bloodwork results, our program offers various features to enhance your health and wellness journey:
                    </p>

                    <ul class="list-unstyled text-muted mb-5">
                        <li>✔️ - AI Assistance: The AI helps set personalized goals, diet plans, and workout routines based on your bloodwork.</li>
                        <li>✔️ - Supplement Recommendations: Receive suggestions for supplements based on your unique health needs.</li>
                        <li>✔️ - Appointment Reminders: Get reminders when medical appointments are recommended based on your test results.</li>
                        <li>✔️ - Progress Tracking: Compare your current bloodwork results with past ones, giving you a clear picture of your health progression.</li>
                        <li>✔️ - Fasting & BMI Tracker: Keep track of your fasting and monitor your BMI with built-in tools.</li>
                    </ul>

                    <p class="text-muted">
                        Overall, our program combines medical insights, AI-driven guidance, and personalized recommendations to help users make more informed choices about their health.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-success mt-5 text-center">Our Location</h2>

    <div class="map-container mt-4 text-center">
        <div style="border: 2px solid #28a745; border-radius: 10px; overflow: hidden; display: inline-block;">
